rmierung der spätantiken Lebenswelt und Kultur einen besonderen Stellenwert beanspruchen.  aThe first modern, text-critical edition of the Epistula ad Marcellinum by Athanasius of Alexandria presents all of the transmitted manuscripts including the Oriental versions.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Greek, Ancient (to 1453).0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aTheologyvEarly works to 1800. 0aTheologyxHistoryyEarly church, ca. 30-600. 4aAltertumswisssenschaften. 4aAthanasius. 4aTextedition. 7aRELIGION / Christianity / History.2bisacsh  aAthansius.  aClassical Studies.  atext edition.1 aSavvidis, Kyriakos, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWyrwa, Dietmar, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2021z9783110753974oZDB-23-DGF0 cprintz978311070317740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311070516440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110705164423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110705164/original  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2021  aZDB-23-DGGb2021